{"data":[{"date":"07:04 17/06","title":"Mourinho v\u1ebd ra k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng cho Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi \u1edf World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/mourinho-ve-ra-kich-ban-khong-tuong-cho-ronaldo-va-messi-o-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Man Utd m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Argentina, v\u1edbi Ronaldo vs Messi chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 \u1edf lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng\u2026</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u1ea3 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 Argentina \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u00e0 Cristiano Ronaldo n\u00f3i ri\u00eang l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Nam M\u1ef9 c\u1ee7a Lionel Messi.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-chi-co-the-va-mai-luon-la-anh-cristiano-ronaldo-421-188617.html\" target=\"_blank\">B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha th\u1ee7 h\u00f2a \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-3</span> k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh nh\u1edd c\u00fa hat-trick si\u00eau h\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a CR7, trong khi Argentina b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ecb t\u00e2n binh Iceland c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n 1-1 v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh M10 s\u1eafm vai t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 \u1edf qu\u1ea3 penalty h\u1ecfng \u0103n v\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mourinho m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 Ronaldo vs Messi chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Mourinho m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 Ronaldo vs Messi chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/mourinho-ve-ra-kich-ban-khong-tuong-cho-ronaldo-va-messi-o-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Mourinho m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 Ronaldo vs Messi chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Ronaldo \u0111ang t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi th\u1eafng th\u1ebf Messi \u1edf World Cup 2018, trong khi ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng vinh quang ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc cho c\u1ea3 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 Argentina h\u1eb5ng c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t d\u00e0i. Tuy nhi\u00ean chi\u1ebfu tr\u00ean quan \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Jose Mourinho c\u1ee7a CR7, c\u1ea3 hai r\u1ed3i s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft trong m\u01a1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 theo d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n c\u1ee7a HLV \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u1ec7m Man Utd, Argentina c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng C r\u1ed3i l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng knock-out v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng v\u1eadt c\u1ea3n bao g\u1ed3m Australia, T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 \u0110\u1ee9c, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i h\u1ecd trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2014. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng B s\u1ebd h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Uruguay, Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 Brazil<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady, HLV \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Man Utd c\u00f2n v\u1ebd ra vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng cho \u0111\u1ec9nh cao m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Ronaldo vs Messi chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1eb7c Bi\u1ec7t Mourinho:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cHai c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00e1n k\u1ebft s\u1ebd l\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Brazil v\u00e0 Argentina vs \u0110\u1ee9c. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00f3i t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn theo c\u1ea3m x\u00fac v\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i \u01b0u \u00e1i B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i cho tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Argentina c\u0169ng s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3 th\u00f9 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf World Cup 2014 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u1ede tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng ba, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c tr\u1ea3 th\u00f9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng n\u1eefa, v\u1eady n\u00ean Brazil s\u1ebd th\u1eafng \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Argentina s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc qua th\u1eddi gian hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u, v\u1edbi Ronaldo vs Messi \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. \u0110\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y th\u00ec t\u00f4i s\u1ebd b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cho c\u00e1c anh t\u1ef1 t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng!\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-chi-co-the-va-mai-luon-la-anh-cristiano-ronaldo-421-188617.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-chi-co-the-va-mai-luon-la-anh-cristiano-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-chi-co-the-va-mai-luon-la-anh-cristiano-ronaldo-421-188617.html\">B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha: Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 m\u00e3i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 anh, Cristiano Ronaldo!</span><br>\r\nBa b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha r\u1ef1c s\u00e1ng Sochi, Cristiano Ronaldo thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp c\u00fa hat-trick th\u1ee9 51, trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed 88 n\u0103m c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 World Cup c\u0169ng nh\u01b0...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"260","checkdouble":"188683"},{"date":"07:20 17/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL (17h00 ng\u00e0y 17/6): T\u00ecm l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/nhan-dinh-shb-da-nang-vs-hagl-17h00-ngay-176-tim-lai-chien-thang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u HAGL t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n H\u00f2a Xu\u00e2n v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng HLV Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Yao Hermann Kouassi. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o v\u1eeba chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y sau 7 n\u0103m ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Thai-League.</h2><h2>SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ngo\u1ea1i binh t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Thai-League,\u00a0<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Yao Hermann Kouassi</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o l\u00fac 17h00 chi\u1ec1u nay, CLB SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 14 V-League tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1eb7p c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL. Sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u00f4ng H\u00e0n l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, qua \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean BXH.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng tr\u00ecnh ngo\u1ea1i binh Thai-League \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p HAGL  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng tr\u00ecnh ngo\u1ea1i binh Thai-League \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p HAGL  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/shb-da-nang-trinh-hang-thaileague-o-tran-gap-hagl.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u00e2n binh Yao Hermann Kouassi \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p  HAGL?. \u1ea2nh: Bongda.com.vn</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u00f4ng H\u00e0n c\u0169ng s\u1ebd tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat m\u00e0 h\u1ecd v\u1eeba chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 t\u1eeb Thai-League, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 Yao Hermann Kouassi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kouassi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 7 n\u0103m ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Th\u00e1i Lan. Anh t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho CLB Air Force Central t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Thai Division League (Thai-League 2) v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2011 v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y l\u00ean ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Thai-League 1 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2014, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gia nh\u1eadp Chiangmai, Bangkok v\u00e0 Samut Sakhon.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 cao 1m67 nh\u01b0ng b\u00f9 l\u1ea1i Kouassi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t sung m\u00e3n. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y c\u00f2n cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u0103n b\u00e0n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi 61 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 136 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho CLB Air Force Central, m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 t\u1ec7. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Kouassi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd san s\u1ebb g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng c\u00f9ng \u0110\u1ed7 Merlo v\u00e0 H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh ngo\u1ea1i binh c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Diogo \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u1edbi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng \u0111ang g\u1ea5p r\u00fat ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft nh\u01b0 kh\u00e1m s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf (ITC) \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ecbp \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd Yao Hermann Kouassi \u1edf cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n HAGL v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y mai. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-shb-da-nang-vs-hagl-17h00-ngay-176-tim-lai-chien-thang-168-188684.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/nhan-dinh-shb-da-nang-vs-hagl-17h00-ngay-176-tim-lai-chien-thang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-shb-da-nang-vs-hagl-17h00-ngay-176-tim-lai-chien-thang-168-188684.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL (17h00 ng\u00e0y 17/6): T\u00ecm l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</span><br>\r\nC\u1ea3 SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Do \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:#081f2c;mso-fareast-language:=\"\" ko\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"259","checkdouble":"188684"},{"date":"07:51 17/06","title":"B\u1ecb c\u1eaft m\u1ea1ch b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, HAGL th\u1eaft ch\u1eb7t k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt m\u00f9a World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/14/hagl-that-chat-ky-luat-mua-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai HAGL m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng quy \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t nghi\u00eam ng\u1eb7t m\u00f9a World Cup nh\u1eb1m h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9c khuya xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c.</h2><h2>HAGL th\u1eaft ch\u1eb7t k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt m\u00f9a World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">VCK World Cup 2018 di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00f9ng v\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG V-League b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o giai \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng nh\u1ea5t. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eeba chung vui xem World Cup v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t CLB HAGL c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u201cthi\u1ebft qu\u00e2n lu\u1eadt\u201d trong th\u1eddi gian di\u1ec5n ra World Cup 2018. Theo \u0111\u00f3, HAGL c\u1ea5m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1ee9c khuya xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 sinh ho\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn theo khu\u00f4n ph\u00e9p b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HAGL th\u1eaft ch\u1eb7t k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt m\u00f9a World Cup 2018  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HAGL th\u1eaft ch\u1eb7t k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt m\u00f9a World Cup 2018  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/3/HAGL-that-chat-ky-luat-mua-World-Cup-2018--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m th\u1ee9c khuya xem World Cup 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n Anh c\u1ee7a CLB HAGL cho bi\u1ebft BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ec9 cho ph\u00e9p c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xem nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1edbm t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018: \u201cTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi World Cup 2018 kh\u1edfi tranh, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eafng nghe nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u0110a ph\u1ea7n c\u00e1c em \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t xem c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn s\u1edbm, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u mu\u1ed9n v\u00e0o h\u00f4m sau\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng T\u1ea5n Anh vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea5m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xem c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u mu\u1ed9n \u1edf World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u thi\u1ec7t th\u00f2i, song to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u1edfi l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c t\u1ea1i V.League. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \u201cC\u00e1c em c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c r\u00f5 t\u1eadp trung cho V-League m\u1edbi l\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng, xem World Cup c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem tr\u1ecdn c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00f9 h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n, nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf \u0111\u00fang l\u00e0 thi\u1ec7t th\u00f2i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay qu\u00e1 d\u00e0y, l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9, n\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e0nh kh\u1eaft khe v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n xem World Cup. Do \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn s\u1edbm l\u00fac 7 gi\u1edd, 8 gi\u1edd t\u1ed1i th\u00ec c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp trung xem c\u00f9ng nhau, nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3 th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 t\u1ed5 ki\u1ec3m tra \u0111\u1ec3 xem c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00fang lu\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng. CLB kh\u00f4ng cho ph\u00e9p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e1y t\u00ednh b\u1ea3ng, \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 vi ph\u1ea1m CLB s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng k\u1ec9 lu\u1eadt n\u1eb7ng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00f3. Tuy nhi\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1eb7t tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o \u00fd th\u1ee9c t\u1ef1 gi\u00e1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c em\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u nay, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng t\u1ea1i H\u00f2a Xu\u00e2n. \u1ede 3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u00f4ng H\u00e0n, v\u00ec th\u1ebf c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u00e0 b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-shb-da-nang-vs-hagl-17h00-ngay-176-tim-lai-chien-thang-168-188684.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/nhan-dinh-shb-da-nang-vs-hagl-17h00-ngay-176-tim-lai-chien-thang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-shb-da-nang-vs-hagl-17h00-ngay-176-tim-lai-chien-thang-168-188684.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL (17h00 ng\u00e0y 17/6): T\u00ecm l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</span><br>\r\nC\u1ea3 SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Do \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:#081f2c;=\"\" mso-fareast-language:ko\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"258","checkdouble":"188685"},{"date":"07:53 17/06","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (17/6/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-1762018.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay 17/6 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u00f4ng tin ng\u00e0y gi\u1edd c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 di\u1ec5n ra h\u00f4m nay v\u00e0 \u0111\u00eam/r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y mai.</h2><div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vck-world-cup-2018/lich-thi-dau-41.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/3/Lich_thi_dau_World_Cup_2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vck-world-cup-2018/lich-thi-dau-41.html\"> L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u VCK World Cup 2018 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t</span><br>\r\nC\u1eadp nh\u1eadt nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u VCK World Cup 2018 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 14.6 \u0111\u1ebfn 15.7.2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay 17-6-2018 v\u00e0 r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y mai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay 17-6-2018 v\u00e0 r\u1ea1ng s\u