 style=\"text-align: center;\">17/06 19:00</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">S\u00e0i G\u00f2n - H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"257","checkdouble":"188686"},{"date":"08:28 17/06","title":"SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng tr\u00ecnh ngo\u1ea1i binh Thai-League \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p HAGL?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/shb-da-nang-trinh-hang-thaileague-o-tran-gap-hagl.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u HAGL t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n H\u00f2a Xu\u00e2n v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng HLV Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Yao Hermann Kouassi. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o v\u1eeba chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y sau 7 n\u0103m ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Thai-League.</h2><h2>SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ngo\u1ea1i binh t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Thai-League,\u00a0<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Yao Hermann Kouassi</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o l\u00fac 17h00 chi\u1ec1u nay, CLB SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 14 V-League tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1eb7p c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL. Sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u00f4ng H\u00e0n l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, qua \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean BXH.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng tr\u00ecnh ngo\u1ea1i binh Thai-League \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p HAGL  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng tr\u00ecnh ngo\u1ea1i binh Thai-League \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p HAGL  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/shb-da-nang-trinh-hang-thaileague-o-tran-gap-hagl.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u00e2n binh Yao Hermann Kouassi \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p  HAGL?. \u1ea2nh: Bongda.com.vn</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u00f4ng H\u00e0n c\u0169ng s\u1ebd tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat m\u00e0 h\u1ecd v\u1eeba chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 t\u1eeb Thai-League, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 Yao Hermann Kouassi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kouassi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 7 n\u0103m ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Th\u00e1i Lan. Anh t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho CLB Air Force Central t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Thai Division League (Thai-League 2) v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2011 v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y l\u00ean ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Thai-League 1 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2014, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gia nh\u1eadp Chiangmai, Bangkok v\u00e0 Samut Sakhon.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 cao 1m67 nh\u01b0ng b\u00f9 l\u1ea1i Kouassi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t sung m\u00e3n. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y c\u00f2n cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u0103n b\u00e0n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi 61 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 136 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho CLB Air Force Central, m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 t\u1ec7. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Kouassi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd san s\u1ebb g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng c\u00f9ng \u0110\u1ed7 Merlo v\u00e0 H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh ngo\u1ea1i binh c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Diogo \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u1edbi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng \u0111ang g\u1ea5p r\u00fat ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft nh\u01b0 kh\u00e1m s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf (ITC) \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ecbp \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd Yao Hermann Kouassi \u1edf cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n HAGL v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y mai. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-shb-da-nang-vs-hagl-17h00-ngay-176-tim-lai-chien-thang-168-188684.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/nhan-dinh-shb-da-nang-vs-hagl-17h00-ngay-176-tim-lai-chien-thang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-shb-da-nang-vs-hagl-17h00-ngay-176-tim-lai-chien-thang-168-188684.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL (17h00 ng\u00e0y 17/6): T\u00ecm l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</span><br>\r\nC\u1ea3 SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Do \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:#081f2c;mso-fareast-language:=\"\" ko\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"256","checkdouble":"188687"},{"date":"08:08 17/06","title":"T\u1eeb gi\u1edd, h\u00e3y g\u1ecdi Messi l\u00e0 \"Miss Penalty\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/tu-gio-hay-goi-messi-la-miss-penalty.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1eddi ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch s\u00e2u cay nh\u1ea5t d\u00e0nh cho si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018.</h2>Lionel Messi \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn sau khi \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i chia \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi Iceland \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n World Cup 2018. V\u00ec qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n h\u1ecfng \u0103n n\u00e0y, Messi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ec1 t\u00e0i b\u1ecb d\u00e2n m\u1ea1ng ch\u1ebf \u1ea3nh v\u00e0 nh\u1ea1o b\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong \u0111\u00f3, \"th\u00e2m nho\" nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u00e0n s\u00f3ng k\u00eau g\u1ecdi \u0111\u1eb7t bi\u1ec7t danh m\u1edbi cho Messi l\u00e0 \"Miss Penalty\" (t\u1eeb Miss trong ti\u1ebfng Anh c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 hoa h\u1eadu v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ngh\u0129a kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1).\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/df0lw64waaaosbc-1529164555361572184660-15291646284422035025288.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/3538019017140834453410524149379513962201088n-15291646406571170844120.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra c\u00e1c fan c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng kh\u1ecfi so s\u00e1nh Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo. M\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp hattrick, gi\u00fap B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 3-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc T\u00e2y Ban Nha m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. Trong khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi kia th\u1eadm ch\u00ed s\u00fat h\u1ecfng penalty (c\u1ea7n nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng 1/3 b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean ... ch\u1ea5m 11m).\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/4-1529163972539832576147.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi b\u1ecb ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o sau khi s\u00fat h\u1ecfng 11m tr\u1eadn Argentina 1-1 Iceland h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Messi b\u1ecb ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o sau khi s\u00fat h\u1ecfng 11m tr\u1eadn Argentina 1-1 Iceland h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Messi-bi-che-nhao-sau-khi-sut-hong-11m-tran-Argentina-1-1-Iceland-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo: s\u00fat penalty th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n, l\u1eadp hat-trick. Messi: h\u1ecfng penalty, h\u1ecfng v\u00e0i c\u00fa s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t fan kh\u00e1c th\u00ec ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch vi\u1ebft l\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i Twitter, k\u00e8m theo t\u1ea5m h\u00ecnh Messi \u0111ang k\u00fd l\u00ean m\u1ed9t t\u1edd gi\u1ea5y v\u1edbi n\u1ed9i dung: \"Ch\u00e0o Ronaldo. T\u1edb l\u00e0 Messi \u0111\u00e2y. T\u1edb \u0111ang b\u0103n kho\u0103n kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft l\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n nh\u1ec9? H\u00e3y ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i s\u1edbm cho t\u1edb nh\u00e9\".\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Screen-Shot-2018-06-17-at-1-39-3258-6509-1529177580.png.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ed1ng k\u00ea cho th\u1ea5y Messi \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng b\u1ed1n trong b\u1ea3y qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t (cho Barca v\u00e0 Argentina), t\u1ee9c l\u00e0 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 h\u1ecfng \u0103n l\u00ean t\u1edbi 57%. Danh th\u1ee7 Gary Lineker vi\u1ebft l\u00ean Twitter: \"Messi b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. C\u00f9ng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m, Ronaldo c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111ang nh\u00e1y m\u1eaft tinh ngh\u1ecbch\". <br>\r\n<br>\r\nSi\u00eau sao Argentina tung ra t\u1edbi 11 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn ho\u00e0 Iceland 1-1, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n ghi b\u00e0n. Trong khi Ronaldo ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n b\u1ed1n pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 hat-trick v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2010 - T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ve mat cua Cristiano Ronaldo khi nghe tin Messi vua da hong 1 qua 11 m\" title=\"V\u1ebb m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo khi nghe tin Messi v\u1eeba \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 1 qu\u1ea3 11 m\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/3_4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">V\u1ebb m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo khi nghe tin Messi v\u1eeba \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 1 qu\u1ea3 11 m</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"255","checkdouble":"188688"},{"date":"08:47 17/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Costa Rica vs Serbia (19h ng\u00e0y 17/6): \u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng di\u1ec7t m\u1ed3i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/nhan-dinh-costa-rica-vs-serbia-19h-ngay-176-dai-bang-diet-moi.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Costa Rica vs Serbia c\u1ee7a Bongda24h.vn kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m ngo\u00e0i d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Costa Rica ch\u1ec9 gi\u1ecfi b\u1eaft n\u1ea1t \u201cchi\u1ebfu d\u01b0\u1edbi\u201d</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2014, Costa Rica \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ph\u1ea3i ng\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00ecn khi v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Uruguay, Anh v\u00e0 Italia \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng. T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8, h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Hy L\u1ea1p sau lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i t\u1edbi t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. Ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfc r\u1eb1ng c\u0169ng tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t \u201c\u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang\u201d c\u00e2n n\u00e3o,\u00a0 Costa Rica \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n b\u1edfi H\u00e0 Lan, \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3 chung cu\u1ed9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n4 n\u0103m tr\u00f4i qua, g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 Costa Rica ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 th\u00eam g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t n\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd. V\u1eabn l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t nh\u01b0 Keylor Navas, Bryan Oviedo, Giancarlo Gonz\u00e1lez, Bryan Ruiz r\u1ed3i Christian Bolanos\u2026 V\u00ec th\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i trung b\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t Los Ticos l\u00ean t\u1edbi h\u01a1n 30 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Costa Rica vs Serbia (19h ng\u00e0y 176) \u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng di\u1ec7t m\u1ed3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Costa Rica vs Serbia (19h ng\u00e0y 176) \u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng di\u1ec7t m\u1ed3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/1/Nhan-dinh-Costa-Rica-vs-Serbia-(19h-ngay-176)-Dai-bang-diet-moi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110T\u00a0Costa Rica v\u1eabn l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u0169 k\u1ef9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1eddi l\u1edbn nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi Costa Rica gi\u00e0u b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh tr\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf. Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng 8 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea3 giao h\u1eefu v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, h\u1ecd thua t\u1edbi 6. C\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, 2 tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng thua c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng khu v\u1ef1c CONCACAF l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng B\u1eafc Ireland v\u00e0 Scotland ho\u1eb7c b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n ho\u1eb7c ngang s\u1ee9c. Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Costa Rica vs Serbia c\u0169ng l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean thu\u1ed9c \u201cc\u1eeda d\u01b0\u1edbi\u201d. <br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Serbia v\u1edbi d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSerbia \u0111\u00e3 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf 3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp bao g\u1ed3m Euro 2012 v\u00e0 2016 b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh World Cup 2014. Nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea1i ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh \u201c\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng\u201d \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n, \u00edt nh\u1ea5t c\u0169ng l\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u01a1 s\u1edf cho h\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. T\u1eeb c\u00e1c c\u1ef1u binh Aleksandar Kolarov, Branislav Ivanovic t\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ho\u1eb7c v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00edn nh\u01b0 Adem Ljajic, Nemanja Matic, Aleksandar Mitrovic, Luka Milivojevic, Sergej Milinkovic-Savic, Dusan Tadic\u2026 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Serbia v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i khu v\u1ef1c ch\u00e2u \u00c2u thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sergej milinkovic-savic serbia\" title=\"Sergej milinkovic-savic serbia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/31/8-nhan-to-x-hua-hen-se-toa-sang-o-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Serbia l\u1ea1i ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n10 tr\u1eadn \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i, Serbia ch\u1ec9 thua c\u00f3 1, ghi t\u1edbi 20 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ph\u00eda sau \u00edt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 6 b\u00e0n. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thu\u1ed9c Nam T\u01b0 c\u0169 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 5-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bolivia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i \u00c1o h\u00f4m \u0111\u00f3, Serbia \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n h\u1ebft ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, trong tay HLV Mladen Krstajic c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n \u0111a d\u1ea1ng. Ho\u1eb7c \u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 c\u00e0n l\u01b0\u1edbt c\u1ee7a Kostic, Ljajic hay Tadic. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nHo\u1eb7c Krstajic c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 nh\u1eefng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng ki\u1ec3u nh\u01b0 Costa Rica. Serbia c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat xa l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 Kolarov, Milinkovic-Savic, Milivojevic. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 Ivanovic, Matic hay Mitrovic. \u0110\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n \u201cph\u00e1 b\u00ea t\u00f4ng\u201d h\u1eefu hi\u1ec7u v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn cho Costa Rica e s\u1ee3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-serbia-tai-world-cup-2018-an-so-cua-bang-e-421-188114.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/2/dt-serbia-tai-world-cup-2018-an-so-cua-bang-e.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-serbia-tai-world-cup-2018-an-so-cua-bang-e-421-188114.html\">\u0110T Serbia t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018: \u1ea8n s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng E</span><br>\r\n<span>\u0110T Serbia t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u1ea9n s\u1ed1 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7y t\u00e0i n\u0103ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 v\u00e0 Costa Rica \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng Brazil \u0111i...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb \u0111i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ec1u</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018, Costa Rica thua li\u1ec1n 2 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Anh (0-2) v\u00e0 B\u1ec9 (1-4), th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi 6 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p tung ra \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng cho th\u1ea5y so v\u1edbi 4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 suy gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Serbia c\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 h\u01a1n. H\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u201cch\u00fa ng\u1ef1a \u00f4\u201d t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. M\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Krstajic c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng E v\u1eabn c\u00f2n Brazil v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Costa Rica vs Serbia\" title=\"Preview Costa Rica vs Serbia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Costa-Rica-vs-Serbia.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Costa Rica vs Serbia 19h ng\u00e0y 17/6</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u1edbi Costa Rica v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129, nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Serbia \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i s\u1ebd nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u201c\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng\u201d s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nCosta Rica (5-4-1):</strong> 1.Navas - 16.Gamboa, 3.Gonz\u00e1lez, 2.Acosta, 6.Duarte, 8.Oviedo - 10.Ruiz, 5.Borges, 20.Guzm\u00e1n, 7.Bolanos - 21.Urena.<br>\r\n<strong>Serbia (4-2-3-1):</strong> 1.Stojkovic - 6.Ivanovic, 15.Milenkovic, 3.Tosic, 11.Kolarov - 20.Milinkovic-Savic, 21.Matic - 10.Tadic, 22.Ljajic, 17.Kostic - 9.Mitrovic.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: Serbia th\u1eafng 1-0<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Costa Rica vs Serbia\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Costa Rica vs Serbia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Costa-Rica-vs-Serbia-(5-4-1-vs-4-2-3-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Costa Rica vs Serbia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Serbia v\u00e0 Costa Rica tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-7-nhan-dinh-bang-e-421-188456.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 7: Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ea3ng E</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/danh-sach-cau-thu-doi-tuyen-serbia-tham-du-world-cup-2018-421-187585.html\">Danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Serbia tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/danh-sach-cau-thu-doi-tuyen-costa-rica-tham-du-world-cup-2018-421-187533.html\">Danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Costa Rica tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"254","checkdouble":"188689"},{"date":"08:47 17/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 (1h ng\u00e0y 18/6): Nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng xoay kim \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/nhan-dinh-brazil-vs-thuy-si-1h-ngay-186-nhe-nhang-xoay-kim-dong-ho.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd, k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ec3 nghi ng\u1edd \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 5 l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u1ed1 1 cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 nh\u01b0 Brazil.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Brazil s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho World Cup</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110T Brazil \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi VCK World Cup 2018 c\u00f3 ch\u00fat thi\u1ec7t th\u00f2i khi thi\u1ebfu h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i Dani Alves do ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, Danilo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao PSG \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Selecao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a World Cup tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTo\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i Brazil \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ed9c l\u1ea1i m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 \u0111eo \u0111\u1eb3ng 4 n\u0103m qua. T\u1ea1i World Cup 2014, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Samba d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft song th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i 1-7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi HLV Tite l\u00ean n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n th\u00e1ng 9 n\u0103m 2016, \u0110T Brazil v\u1eabn ch\u00ecm trong b\u1ea5t \u1ed5n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 (1h ng\u00e0y 186) Nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng xoay kim h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 (1h ng\u00e0y 186) Nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng xoay kim h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/10/Nhan-dinh-Brazil-vs-Thuy-Si-(1h-ngay-186)-Nhe-nhang-xoay-kim-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Brazil c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o th\u1eddi gian qua</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBrazil kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u1edf 3 trong s\u1ed1 4 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup, b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng Copa America 2016 d\u1eabn t\u1edbi HLV Dunga b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i. Nh\u01b0ng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, Brazil h\u1ed3i sinh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u00e0 l\u00e0m n\u1ee9c l\u00f2ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9. 10 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, 2 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a trong ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i khu v\u1ef1c Nam M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o v\u00e0ng xanh c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u, gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1edbi VCK World Cup t\u1ea1i Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Brazil \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i 6 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu trong v\u00f2ng n\u1eeda n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. H\u1ecd th\u1eafng t\u1edbi 6 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 h\u00f2a 1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Anh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Wembley. T\u00ednh ra, Brazil \u0111\u00e3 ghi 12 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 1 l\u1ea7n l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi sau 6 tr\u1eadn n\u00f3i tr\u00ean. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00fa ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho VCK World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edbi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neymar cua Brazil\" title=\"Neymar cua Brazil\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/10/brazil-danh-mat-ban-sac-duoi-thoi-tite.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Neymar \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho World Cup</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c c\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u1ed1 1</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 l\u1eabn th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c, Brazil \u0111\u1ec1u x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u1ed1 1 cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi ti\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang x\u1ebfp t\u1eadn th\u1ee9 6 tr\u00ean BXH m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 FIFA cung c\u1ea5p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u01b0\u1edfng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 sau chu\u1ed7i th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u1ea3 khi \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u1eabn giao h\u1eefu. 12 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 th\u1eafng t\u1edbi 10 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a v\u00e0 1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. N\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 t\u00ednh giao h\u1eefu, trong qu\u00e3ng 2 n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1ecd th\u1eafng 5, h\u00f2a 1 sau 6 tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Brazil vs Thuy Sy\" title=\"Preview Brazil vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Brazil-vs-Thuy-Sy.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 1h ng\u00e0y 18/6</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao. D\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Vladimir Petkovic t\u1eebng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i Serie A, h\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, khoa h\u1ecdc, ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc kim \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3. \u1ede chu\u1ed7i 17 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng 2 n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 ch\u1ec9 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u00f3 8 b\u00e0n, gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf 12 tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Brazil \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ef9 cho cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i, h\u1ecd m\u1eddi \u00c1o, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 phong c\u00e1ch t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu. \u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Selecao, nh\u01b0ng sau c\u00f9ng h\u1ecd c\u0169ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thuy Si 0-0 Northern Ireland\" title=\"Thuy Si 0-0 Northern Ireland\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/3/Thuy-Si-0-0-Northern-Ireland.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u00ean t\u1ea7m</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBrazil l\u00fac n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng thi\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1 \u201cb\u00ea t\u00f4ng\u201d. D\u1ec5 \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc r\u1eb1ng Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 s\u1ebd l\u00f9i r\u1ea5t s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ec3 chia c\u1eaft s\u1ef1 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng 5 l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng Brazil \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Neymar, ng\u01b0\u1eddi r\u1ea5t gi\u1ecfi ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ed9c l\u1eadp, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i b\u00f3ng qua m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o r\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh b\u00ean kia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBrazil c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat xa t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 Willian, Philippe Coutinho r\u1ed3i nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 Miranda, Paulinho hay Thiago Silva. \u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Tite d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh h\u1ecd. Ph\u00e1t huy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Brazil s\u1ebd \u0111i r\u1ea5t s\u00e2u th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, d\u00f9 b\u1ea3ng E kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i qu\u00e1 d\u1ec5 th\u1edf v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129, Costa Rica v\u00e0 Serbia \u0111ang ch\u1edd ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Tuy nhi\u00ean, d\u00f9 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Brazil c\u0169ng l\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng. Tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129, 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi t\u1ea7m tay c\u1ee7a \u201cC\u00e1c v\u0169 c\u00f4ng Samba\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nBrazil (4-3-3): </strong>1.Alisson - 14.Danilo, 2.Silva, 3.Miranda, 12.Marcelo - 15.Paulinho, 5.Casemiro, 11.Coutinho - 19.Willian, 9.Jesus, 10.Neymar.<br>\r\n<strong>Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 (4-2-3-1):</strong> 1.Sommer - 2.Lichtsteiner, 22.Schar, 5.Akanji, 13.Rodr\u00edguez - 10.Xhaka, 11.Behrami - 23.Shaqiri, 8.Freuler, 14.Zuber - 9.Seferovic.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: Brazil th\u1eafng 2-0</strong><strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Brazil vs Thuy Sy\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Brazil vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Brazil-vs-Thuy-sy-(4-3-3-vs-4-2-3-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Brazil vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"253","checkdouble":"188691"},{"date":"09:00 17/06","title":"\u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico (22h00 ng\u00e0y 17/6): Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 vua","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/17/duc-vs-mexico-22h00-ngay-176-buoc-dau-cua-nha-vua.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f4ng cu\u1ed9c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ngai v\u00e0ng v\u1edbi hy v\u1ecdng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Mexico, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ed9t n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ecd t\u1eebng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y c\u00fap.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ed1n n\u0103m sau khi gi\u00e0nh c\u00fap tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Brazil, \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u thay \u0111\u1ed5i. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng ghi b\u00e0n trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Mario Goetze c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong danh s\u00e1ch 23 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn Nga h\u00e8 2018.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico (22h00 ng\u00e0y 176) B\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 vua h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico (22h00 ng\u00e0y 176) B\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 vua h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/7/3/Duc-vs-Mexico-(22h00-ngay-176)-Buoc-dau-cua-nha-vua-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Confederations Cup 2017, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean hai \u0111i\u1ec1u gi\u00fap h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng: Nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 Joachim Low.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ec5 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng Joachim Low \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua c\u01a1n \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn ra 23 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn Nga. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, \u00f4ng g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean Leroy Sane v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch, hay khi\u1ebfn Sandro Wagner (Bayern Munich) ph\u1ea3i s\u1edbm tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2020 c\u1ee7a HLV Joachim Low khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c y\u00ean t\u00e2m. HLV Joachim Low l\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac s\u01b0 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Mannschaft trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta hy v\u1ecdng \u00f4ng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c v\u1eadn may \u0111\u00f3 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chinh ph\u1ee5c k\u1ebb ng\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng l\u01b0\u1edbt qua v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch 10 tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n th\u1eafng, ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 43 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi 4 l\u1ea7n. N\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, h\u1ecd n\u00e2ng cao Confederations Cup c\u0169ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga. Tr\u00f9ng h\u1ee3p l\u00e0m sao, Mannschaft t\u1eebng ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Mexico m\u1ed9t n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tai Confederations Cup 2017, DT Duc tung danh bai Mexico voi ti so 4-1.\" title=\"T\u1ea1i Confederations Cup 2017, \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1eebng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Mexico v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 4-1.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/085752-duc-vs-mexico.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>T\u1ea1i Confederations Cup 2017, \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1eebng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Mexico v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 4-1.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u00f3, \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Mexico \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 4-1.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o World Cup 2018, \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 t\u1edbi Nga, Mannschaft ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 1 trong 6 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n v\u1eeba b\u1ecb Nga v\u00f9i d\u1eadp \u0111\u1ebfn 5-0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn khai m\u1ea1c.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 khao kh\u00e1t, c\u1ea7n ch\u1ea5t l\u1eeda\" - Jerome Boateng k\u00eau g\u1ecdi: \"\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 \u1edf m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc, c\u1ea3 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp l\u1eabn c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf t\u1eebng centimet tr\u00ean s\u00e2n\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n \u0110T Mexico hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean cho ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Th\u1ebf n\u00ean th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Juan Carlos Osorio ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t qua t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-4 h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i gi\u00fap \u0110T Mexico r\u00fat ra nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Duc vs Mexico\" title=\"Preview \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/duc-vs-mexico-22h00-ngay-176-buoc-dau-cua-nha-vua.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 x\u00f3a b\u1ecf nh\u1eefng ho\u00e0i nghi.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng F, \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 chi\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng trong. Mexico s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c cho t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. V\u1edbi El Tri, m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u00e2n qu\u00fd, th\u1ebf n\u00ean HLV Juan Carlos Osorio nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd v\u1edbi hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, r\u1ed3i bung s\u1ee9c \u1edf hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u sau.<br>\r\n<strong><br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn:</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 t\u01b0 \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico g\u1eb7p nhau \u1edf World Cup. \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng (6-0 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng n\u0103m 1978, 2-1 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i n\u0103m 1998), c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a (0-0 t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft n\u0103m 1986, sau \u0111\u00f3 th\u1eafng 4-1 \u1edf lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* Mexico ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 1 trong 11 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0110\u1ee9c (h\u00f2a 5, thua 5). \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 2-0 n\u0103m 1985.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* \u0110\u1ee9c th\u1eafng trong t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 b\u1ea3y tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n World Cup g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, ghi 20 b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi 4 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t (8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia n\u0103m 2002, 4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica n\u0103m 2006, 4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Australia n\u0103m 2010, 4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha n\u0103m 2014).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* Mexico b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong 5 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n World Cup g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t (th\u1eafng 4, h\u00f2a 1), tr\u1eadn thua g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Na Uy n\u0103m 1994.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup trong 4 l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, chu\u1ed7i d\u00e0i nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u1edf m\u1ed7i k\u1ef3 tham d\u1ef1 k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1990.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* Mexico c\u0169ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i trong 6 k\u1ef3 World Cup g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tham d\u1ef1, ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 2 trong s\u1ed1 17 tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t (th\u1eafng 8, h\u00f2a 7).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico (22h00 ng\u00e0y 17/6):</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ee9c (4-2-3-1): </strong>1.Neuer - 18.Kimmich, 5.Hummels, 17.Boateng, 3.Hector - 6.Khedira, 8.Kroos - 11.Reus, 13.Muller, 7.Draxler - 9.Werner</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Mexico (4-1-4-1):</strong> 13.Ochoa - 3.Salcedo, 2.H.Ayala, 15.H.Moreno, 23.Gallardo - 16.H.Herrera - 11.Vela, 18.A.Guardado, 10.G.Dos Santos, 22.Lozano - 9.RJimenez</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1: </strong>\u0110\u1ee9c 2-1 Mexico<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Duc vs Mexico\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Duc-vs-Mexico-(4-2-3-1-vs-4-1-4-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ea1t (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"252","checkdouble":"188692"},{"date":"01:49 17/06","title":"B\u1ecb Iceland c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n, Sampaoli v\u1eabn \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o \"t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3\" Messi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/bi-iceland-cam-chan-sampaoli-van-dat-niem-tin-vao-toi-do-messi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Sampaoli k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng Messi s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Argentina v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018 d\u00f9 si\u00eau sao 30 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eeba c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u00ean m\u1ee9c th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda.</h2><h2>Th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda Messi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi Maxi Meza b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y ng\u00e3 trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m, Argentina \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 si\u00eau sao Lionel Messi ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 gi\u00fap Argentina chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Messi l\u1ea1i s\u00fat qu\u00e1 hi\u1ec1n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Hannes Halldorsson tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t 11 m\u00e9t. Trong 30 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/argentina-vs-iceland-bang-d-463-188637.html\" target=\"_blank\">Argentina vs Iceland</span>, M10 \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng s\u1eeda sai nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Chung cu\u1ed9c, Argentina b\u1ecb Iceland c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u1ecb Iceland c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n, Sampaoli v\u1eabn \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda Messi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u1ecb Iceland c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n, Sampaoli v\u1eabn \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda Messi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/bi-iceland-cam-chan-sampaoli-van-dat-niem-tin-vao-toi-do-messi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Messi ch\u01a1i th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i n\u1ed5i h\u1ed3i c\u00f2i k\u1ebft th\u00fac, Messi t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 bu\u1ed3n b\u1ef1c. Tuy v\u1eady, HLV Sampaoli tin t\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1eb1ng Messi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau v\u1ea5p ng\u00e3 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 b\u1edfi v\u00ec Iceland ch\u1ec9 ch\u01a1i b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n Messi h\u1ebft m\u1ee9c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 gi\u00fap Argentina. T\u00f4i vui m\u1eebng v\u00ec t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5y quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u01b0a Argentina v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a Messi l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Sampaoli ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u00ec \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Argentina \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland nh\u01b0ng g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. V\u00e0 Sampaoli ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Argentina \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu khi \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m cao v\u00e0 \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn. Iceland \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ea1o ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 nhanh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 trong hi\u1ec7p hai. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 Iceland ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u01a1i l\u1ec7ch tr\u00e1i. Ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 kh\u00e2u lu\u00e2n chuy\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i qu\u00e1 ch\u1eadm.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng thi\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng pha di chuy\u1ec3n x\u1ed9c th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb tuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7. M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 mang \u0111\u1ebfn qu\u1ea3 penalty cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Argentina vs Iceland (B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018):</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/16/Argentina-1-1-Iceland.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Argentina vs Iceland:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-argentina-vs-iceland-khi-messi-nem-3-diem-ra-duong-421-188661.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn Argentina vs Iceland: Khi Messi n\u00e9m 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thu-mon-iceland-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-can-pha-messi-tren-cham-11m-421-188669.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Iceland ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 Messi tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"251","checkdouble":"188666"},{"date":"00:35 17/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-phap-21-australia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea3ng C VCK World Cup 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n- \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 VCK World Cup th\u1ee9 4 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n (th\u1eafng 2, thua 2).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i VCK World Cup l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Senegal (0-1) n\u0103m 2002.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Australia \u0111\u00e3 thua 4 trong 5 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n World Cup c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2006.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Pogba-cung-dong-doi-Phap-an-mung-ban-thang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pogba \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n- Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ec9 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf 1 trong s\u1ed1 7 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf v\u1eeba qua, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc CH Ireland h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 5.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- C\u1ea3 4 pha c\u1ee9u thua c\u1ee7a Mat Ryan tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p t\u1edbi sau 8 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Australia th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi sau 2 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch ti\u1ebfp theo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- 2 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi \u1edf tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia ch\u1ec9 c\u00e1ch nhau c\u00f3 4 ph\u00fat 7 gi\u00e2y, qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn nh\u1ea5t gi\u1eefa 2 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u World Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u World Cup \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb Senegal vs Uruguay n\u0103m 2002 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n trong th\u1eddi gian ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Ph\u00e1p b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong c\u1ea3 18 tr\u1eadn m\u00e0 Antoine Griezmann ghi b\u00e0n (th\u1eafng 16, h\u00f2a 2).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- \u0110\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i trung b\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t Ph\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc Australia (24 tu\u1ed5i 196 ng\u00e0y) l\u00e0 tr\u1ebb nh\u1ea5t trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u World Cup k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 7 n\u0103m 1930 v\u1edbi Chile.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Daniel Arzani \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u1ea5t ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup cho \u0110T Australia (19 tu\u1ed5i 163 ng\u00e0y).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sam-vai-nguoi-hung-ngay-ra-quan-pogba-nhan-toi-tap-loi-khen-421-188659.html\">S\u1eafm vai ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, Pogba nh\u1eadn t\u1edbi t\u1ea5p l\u1eddi khen</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/gianh-chien-thang-vat-va-griezmann-noi-gi-421-188656.html\">Gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3, Griezmann n\u00f3i g\u00ec</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-phap-21-australia-bang-c-world-cup-2018-461-188652.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia (B\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-phap-vs-australia-bang-c-hom-nay-421-188645.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Ph\u00e1p vs Australia tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/phap-vs-australia-bang-c-463-188624.html\">Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia (KT): Si\u00eau sao l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng, Ph\u00e1p ra qu\u00e2n th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"250","checkdouble":"188667"},{"date":"02:46 17/06","title":"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Iceland ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 Messi tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/thor.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Man Utd kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t pha \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed5ng quan t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t, Paul Pogba v\u1eabn l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u Ph\u00e1p kh\u1ecfi tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a b\u1ebd m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi \u201cqu\u00e2n xanh\u201d Australia trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a anh c\u0169ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i may m\u1eafn, khi c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m trong t\u01b0 t\u1ebf v\u1edbi v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i th\u00f2 ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Aziz Behich t\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f3 v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Mathew Ryan bay ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho \u0111\u00f2i t\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f4ng lao Pogba ghi b\u00e0n tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mourinho \u0111\u00f2i t\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f4ng lao Pogba ghi b\u00e0n tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/mourinho-doi-tuoc-ban-thang-cua-tro-cung-pogba.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho \u0111\u00f2i t\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f4ng lao Pogba ghi b\u00e0n tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh cho Pogba nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh v\u00ec t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, HLV Jose Mourinho kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t pha \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha sau tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/phap-vs-australia-bang-c-463-188624.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia</span>:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTheo t\u00f4i \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u00ednh cho Pogba, \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t pha \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0. D\u00f9 sao, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn c\u00f4ng lao c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p d\u1eabn v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0103n b\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u00f3.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i th\u00edch c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch Ph\u00e1p ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ef1 do Griezmann, Mbappe v\u00e0 Dembele. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 tin ch\u01a1i m\u1ea1nh d\u1ea1n, m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m h\u01a1n, thay v\u00ec h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf pressing gi\u00fap Australia c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, th\u1ea3nh th\u01a1i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u1ea7u xu\u00f4i \u0111u\u00f4i l\u1ecdt m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3, m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p v\u1eefng tin h\u01a1n tr\u00ean ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, v\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t. Th\u1ee9 n\u0103m n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Didier Deschamps s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Peru trong l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Highlights tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia:<br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/16/Phap-2-1-Australia.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"249","checkdouble":"188669"},{"date":"02:09 17/06","title":"Messi nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Argentina","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/messi-nhan-loi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-argentina.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Messi m\u1edbi l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i sau khi Argentina b\u1ecb Iceland c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a cay \u0111\u1eafng trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n \u1edf World Cup 2018.</h2><h2>Argentina b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Argentina t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a 1-1 v\u1edbi Iceland. Sergio Aguero \u0111\u01b0a La Albiceleste v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 19. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Alfred Finnbogason \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed khi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho Iceland \u1edf m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup ch\u1ec9 4 ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede hi\u1ec7p hai, Messi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Argentina gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Halldorsson. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Messi c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 tung ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 11 c\u00fa s\u00fat m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Messi nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/messi-nhan-loi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-argentina.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Messi nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Argentina tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Argentina \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i v\u1ec1 m\u00ecnh. Nh\u01b0ng anh c\u0169ng hy v\u1ecdng c\u00e1c C\u0110V kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 ph\u1eabn n\u1ed9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o s\u1ecdc tr\u1eafng xanh m\u1edbi gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cH\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Iceland qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 khoan th\u1ee7ng. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n l\u00f9i s\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady. Qu\u1ea3 penalty khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m ph\u1ea3i xin l\u1ed7i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u00ean l\u00ean v\u00ec k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i. Ch\u00fang ta x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Ch\u00fang ta v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9. Nh\u01b0ng l\u00fac n\u00e0y, \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<p>\u00a0</p>\r\n<h2>Messi \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfp</h2>\r\n<p>Messi c\u00f3 v\u1ebb kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 duy\u00ean v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t penalty. Hi\u1ec7n gi\u1edd, ng\u00f4i sao 30 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 4/7 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t cho CLB c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng v\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u00e0 Messi t\u1ecf ra bi quan. Trong ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, M10 c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo trong <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-bang-d-world-cup-2018-can-than-day-argentina-462-187893.html\" target=\"_blank\">b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018</span> g\u1eb7p Croatia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201c\u0110\u00e2y m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua th\u1eadt t\u1ec7 v\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n so v\u1edbi Iceland. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Croatia \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Argentina vs Iceland:<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/bi-iceland-cam-chan-sampaoli-van-dat-niem-tin-vao-toi-do-messi-469-188666.html\">B\u1ecb Iceland c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n, Sampaoli v\u1eabn \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thu-mon-iceland-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-can-pha-messi-tren-cham-11m-421-188669.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Iceland ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 Messi tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nXu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"248","checkdouble":"188670"},{"date":"02:48 17/06","title":"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Croatia vs Nigeria tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/ket-qua-croatia-vs-nigeria-bang-d.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Croatia vs Nigeria tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay. Th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n, di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn ch\u00ednh, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Croatia vs Nigeria b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 02h00 \u0111\u00eam ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 17/6.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 chung cu\u1ed9c Croatia vs Nigeria: 2-0<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<strong>Ghi b\u00e0n: </strong>Etebo (32', ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi), Modric (70')<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/17/H1-Croatia-vs-Nigeria.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\">\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/17/Croatia-2-0-Nigeria.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Argentina b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland, cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n gi\u1eefa Croatia vs Nigeria \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh l\u00ean m\u1ed9t b\u1eadc. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng, v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh cho m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn di\u1ec5n ra r\u1ea5t h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn ngay trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCroatia \u0111\u00e3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t t\u1ed1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, v\u1edbi tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nguy hi\u1ec3m. \u0110\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 32, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o s\u1ecdc ca-ro \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 kh\u00e1 may m\u1eafn, xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c, Mario Mandzukic \u0111\u00e3 bay ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u, b\u00f3ng v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh ch\u1ea1m ch\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Etebo v\u00e0 bay v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Nigeria. M\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng may m\u1eafn do \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 Croatia n\u1eafm ch\u00fat l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf sau 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ban mo ty so trong tran Croatia vs Nigeria\" title=\"B\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 trong tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Nigeria\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/etbo.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>B\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 trong tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Nigeria</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p 2, th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec thay \u0111\u1ed5i. Croatia v\u1eabn n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn, trong khi Nigeria t\u1eadp trung ch\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee1 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn, Luka Modric n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-0 \u1edf ph\u00fat 70 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, khi h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Nigeria m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng. Ekong trong m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i, khi\u1ebfn \u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh ch\u1ecbu qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1i c\u00e3i.</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ban thang cua Modric Croatia vs Nigeria\" title=\"B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Modric Croatia vs Nigeria\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/modric.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Modric trong tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Nigeria 2-0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi. V\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, \u0110T Croatia t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D, trong khi Nigeria b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc ca-ro s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi Argentina, trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, \u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh sau tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng su\u00f4n s\u1ebb, c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t \u00edt c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"247","checkdouble":"188671"},{"date":"03:13 17/06","title":"Mourinho \u0111\u00f2i t\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng Pogba","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/mourinho-doi-tuoc-ban-thang-cua-tro-cung-pogba.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Man Utd kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t pha \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed5ng quan t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t, Paul Pogba v\u1eabn l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u Ph\u00e1p kh\u1ecfi tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a b\u1ebd m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi \u201cqu\u00e2n xanh\u201d Australia trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a anh c\u0169ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i may m\u1eafn, khi c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m trong t\u01b0 t\u1ebf v\u1edbi v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i th\u00f2 ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Aziz Behich t\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f3 v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Mathew Ryan bay ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho \u0111\u00f2i t\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f4ng lao Pogba ghi b\u00e0n tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mourinho \u0111\u00f2i t\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f4ng lao Pogba ghi b\u00e0n tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/mourinho-doi-tuoc-ban-thang-cua-tro-cung-pogba.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho \u0111\u00f2i t\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f4ng lao Pogba ghi b\u00e0n tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh cho Pogba nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh v\u00ec t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, HLV Jose Mourinho kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t pha \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha sau tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/phap-vs-australia-bang-c-463-188624.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia</span>:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTheo t\u00f4i \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u00ednh cho Pogba, \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t pha \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0. D\u00f9 sao, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn c\u00f4ng lao c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p d\u1eabn v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0103n b\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u00f3.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i th\u00edch c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch Ph\u00e1p ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ef1 do Griezmann, Mbappe v\u00e0 Dembele. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 tin ch\u01a1i m\u1ea1nh d\u1ea1n, m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m h\u01a1n, thay v\u00ec h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf pressing gi\u00fap Australia c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, th\u1ea3nh th\u01a1i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u1ea7u xu\u00f4i \u0111u\u00f4i l\u1ecdt m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3, m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p v\u1eefng tin h\u01a1n tr\u00ean ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, v\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t. Th\u1ee9 n\u0103m n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Didier Deschamps s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Peru trong l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Highlights tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia:<br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/16/Phap-2-1-Australia.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"246","checkdouble":"188673"}]}